body_html: Looks like you may need a dependency on the head py_library from the estimators py_library. Not that you have to, but you can also run these tests locally with "bazel run //tensorflow/contrib/timeseries/python/timeseries:head_test" (or go to the directory and just specify :head_test). If that's passing you can run all of the timeseries tests locally with "bazel test //tensorflow/contrib/timeseries/...".
